<div class="cntPage">
<h1>Library Services</h1><h3 class="notmobile">Our vision is to create a library of excellence in support of the needs of a world-class, competitive, academic health sciences centre.</h3>
<p>The library facilitates a full range of high quality values-based, patient-centered services that support leadership in seven priority program areas, medical education and research.</p>
<p>While our mandate is to serve the information needs of our professional staff members, patients and family members are also welcome to use our consumer health collection and other resources on site. Computers with web access are available in the libraries for education and research purpose only.</p>
<p class="p1">If you require more information or need information in another format, please e-mail <a href="mailto:accessibility@sunnybrook.ca">accessibility@sunnybrook.ca</a> or call 416.480.4040 and tell us what you require &ndash;&nbsp;we will work with you to meet your needs.</p>
<h2 class="p1">Library Services patient &amp; family education resources:</h2>
<ul>
<li class="p1"><a href="content/?page=books-cancer-patient-education">Cancer</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Locations and hours:</h2>
<p><strong>Sunnybrook R. Ian Macdonald Library</strong><br />Location: <a href="content/?page=hospital-directions-map-address-parking-transit">Bayview Campus</a>, room EG-29 <br />Phone: 416-480-4562<br />Hours: Monday to Friday, 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. / weekends and stat. holidays, closed</p>
<p><strong>Holland Centre Library</strong><br />Location: <a href="content/?page=holland-centre-directions-map-address-transit">Holland Centre</a>, room 235<br />Phone: 416-967-8545<br />Hours: Monday to Friday 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.&nbsp; (staffed Monday, Wednesday and Friday) / weekends and stat. holidays, closed</p>
<p><strong>St. John's Rehab Virtual Library</strong><br />Location: <a href="content/?page=st-johns-rehab-address-map-directions-parking">St. John's Rehab</a>,&nbsp;room S-325<br />Phone: 416-480-4562<br />Hours: Monday to&nbsp;Friday 7:00 a.m. to 6:00 p.m.</p>
